  "title": "The Morning After",
  "summary": "The morning after a bloody battle, the wrecked Meltdown Cafe on Nar Shaddaa remains strewn with corpses as the Sith Darth Malign, operating under the alias Tatooine Bob, and his crook ally Dareus take stock amid ongoing street fighting. They are joined by the mercenaries Via, the pirate Juran, the Wookiee Joworral, and the Twi'leks Ka'una and Song, all marked for death by Grubba the Hutt for instigating the uprising. Over passed flasks and cigarettes, the group discusses their tenuous control of the streets, the threat of elite swoop gangs and a Hutt mercenary fleet, and the prospect of looting Grubba's palace once he is dead and the crime lord Thanos installed. Malign declines air support, instead tasking Juran with rigging swoops for a ground assault and setting a rendezvous at the sidedeck on level 72 in four hours before vanishing into the chaos. Juran recruits Dareus to help build the swoops, and the crew settles in to wait out the war.",
